对于双重國籍的巴西公民，可以持有他國的護照以及任何證明巴西國籍的文件（例如巴西身份證或巴西護照過期）进出巴西。<ref>[http://www.pf.gov.br/institucional/ouvidoria/orientacoes-frequentes/brasileiros-com-passaporte-de-outro-pais Brazilians with a passport of another country] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pf.gov.br/institucional/ouvidoria/orientacoes-frequentes/brasileiros-com-passaporte-de-outro-pais |date=20201111234506 }}, [[Federal_Police_of_Brazil|Federal Police of Brazil]], 8 May 2018. {{pt icon}}</ref>如果他們不提供此類文件，則他們仍可以外國人身份進入巴西，但要遵守巴西簽證政策。<ref>[http://www.pf.gov.br/servicos-pf/passaporte/scripts-de-atendimento-passaporte/duvidas-sobre-uso-de-passaporte-estrangeiro-para-brasileiros-com-dupla-nacionalidade Questions about the use of a foreign passport for Brazilians with dual nationality] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pf.gov.br/servicos-pf/passaporte/scripts-de-atendimento-passaporte/duvidas-sobre-uso-de-passaporte-estrangeiro-para-brasileiros-com-dupla-nacionalidade |date=20190919141220 }}, Federal Police of Brazil, 22 August 2018. {{pt icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.romapravoce.com/entrar-e-sair-do-brasil-com-passaporte-estrangeiro/ Dual citizenship: enter and leave Brazil with a foreign passport] {{Wayback|url=http://www.romapravoce.com/entrar-e-sair-do-brasil-com-passaporte-estrangeiro/ |date=20190706063131 }}, Rome for You, 22 August 2018. {{pt icon}}</ref>但是，通常只有在持有人的其他國籍不需要的簽證入境巴西時，這種情況才有可能。巴西僅在特殊情況下才会向具有双重國籍的巴西公民簽發簽證，例如那些在外國政府工作而禁止使用巴西護照的人。<ref>[http://miami.itamaraty.gov.br/en-us/vivis.xml Visitor visa] {{Wayback|url=http://miami.itamaraty.gov.br/en-us/vivis.xml |date=20200716231449 }}, Consulate General of Brazil in Miami.</ref>

